	To faithfully comply with Section 11.2.4 of the Revised IRR of RA 9184 & GPPB NPM No. 075-2017 in the granting of Honoraria to BAC through submitting complete supporting documents as proof of attendance and nature of completed projects claimed to warrant grant;
