	Submit justification why the ₱151,001.00 deficiency will not be subjected to disallowance.

We recommended to Management through the Municipal Treasurer to:
a.	Instruct Mr. Joel D. Pangilinan and Mr. Eref Jun Del U. Ubalde to submit a written explanation as to the delay in his remittances of collections; 
b.	Instruct Mr. Pangilinan to submit a written justification as to the accountable forms not issued in chronological order; 
